Paper: hep-th/9907062

Date: 1999-07-08

Title: Comments on a Covariant Entropy Conjecture

Authors: David A. Lowe

Comments: 7 pages, 2 figures, harvmac, epsf

Journal-ref: JHEP 9910 (1999) 026

Recently Bousso conjectured the entropy crossing a certain light-likehypersurface is bounded by the surface area. We point out a number ofdifficulties with this conjecture.